Title: Lisp / X Demo
Body: MIME-Version: 1.0 Server: CERN/3.0 Date: Tuesday, 07-Jan-97 15:25:46 GMT Content-Type: text/html Content-Length: 1365 Lisp / X Demo Demonstration of Interactive X Graphics from Lisp This is a demo of the X Interface for Gnu Common Lisp which is available as free software under the Gnu General Public License from ftp.ma.utexas.edu When the demo is started, a window is created and some things are drawn in it.
